s:647:"<h5></h5><ul><li>We would now like to ask you to do a rather different task.</li></ul><ul><li>We would like to know how good or bad your health was <u>BEFORE YOUR HIP FRACTURE</u>. To help you say how good or bad your health state is we would like you to try to picture in your mind a scale that looks a bit like a thermometer. The best health state you can imagine is marked 100 (one hundred) at the top of the scale and the worst state you can imagine is marked 0 (zero) at the bottom.</li></ul><ul><li>We would now like you to tell us the point on this scale where you would put your own health state right BEFORE YOUR HIP FRACTURE.</li></ul>";